{"tid":2182774,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[第一次開post] 西裝、皮鞋、皮件討論帖 (37)","createTime":"2020-08-31T13:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T17:24:43.000Z","uid":47773,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"46ebf4d6a7099110ed3de459b9cf7ff7f6db01c1","tid":2182774,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:50:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>由舊登到而家，相信大家都對呢個皮鞋post有上下嘅印象同概念，基本上呢個post希望可以比到大家係連登入面有個地方可以交流對classic menswear（如西裝或皮鞋），皮具及保養（我見之前嘅post有巴打問過如workboot都歡迎交流心得經驗），以至grooming嘅心得。係開始呢個post前，希望新入黎嘅巴打可以花小小時間睇咗第一個post啲資訊先，而如果你可以追翻之前嘅post就更佳。</strong><br />\n<br />\n首先係討論之前，希望大家可以將心比心，睇睇下面既幾條規則，令討論氣氛可以更好︰<br />\n<br />\n1. 和和氣氣，唔好嘈交，理性討論，無論打扮、工藝上都可以傾。<br />\n<br />\n2. 希望各位新朋友可以將第一個post 入面第一頁既內容先睇一睇，有個基本認知，會比較好討論。<br />\n<br />\n3. 此PO歡迎提供折扣資訊、購買方式等討論，如果有買錯Size之類，係度搵人轉手可以接受，但請唔好明目張膽做生意。<br />\n<br />\n4. 討論時也不妨附上照片，好讓巴打們可以判斷到底是甚麼情況，也免去了「有心人」惡意攻擊對手或打手蓄意「吹捧」店鋪的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">【舊post連結：】</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/5577/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/5577/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/77665/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/77665/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/119111/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/119111/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/148033/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/148033/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/243826/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/243826/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/291827/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/291827/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/343941/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/343941/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/377765/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/377765/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/413585/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://li